About the clinic:
Zeiders Orthopedics, PLLC was established in 2016 and specializes in general orthopedics and trauma care. The practice provides comprehensive evaluation and treatment for patients of all ages, offering experienced, patient-centered care in a welcoming environment. A wide range of insurance plans are accepted, including Workers’ Compensation and third-party cases.
With an experienced physician and knowledgeable staff, the clinic is equipped with in-office X-ray and ultrasound services for convenient, efficient diagnosis and treatment. Zeiders Orthopedics also offers affordable PRP (platelet-rich plasma) injections, providing patients with advanced, non-surgical treatment options to support healing and recovery.

